    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Stoliczia setoiyenica, new species, holotype, male (36.7 × 28.5 mm) (ZRC 2023.0411), Thailand.A, overall dorsal habitus; B, dorsal view of carapace; C, frontal view of cephalothorax; D, antennules, antennae and epistome; E, chelae." ;
